tag name|||Gossamer
tag jj|||A kinetic sculpture that builds on the geometric work I've done over the last few years (Polyhydra) and attempts to fuse it with a more natural, optical rendering style. It is currently on display at the Museum of Other Realities.  The soundtrack is a collaboration between James Rampton and Alan Jackson and they really deserve equal billing as the audio is a crucial part of this piece. The particle based bokeh was derived from the incredible work of Keijiro Takahashi
